==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yī bù cuò, bù bù cuò

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[步]][[錯]]，[[步]][[步]][[錯]]'''

# If the ones in front make a misstep, then all the ones following will likewise make a misstep.

===Alternate forms===
[[一步错，步步错]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

